\title{Binding Sites of Deprotonated Citric Acid and Ethylenediaminetetraacetic Acid in the Chelation with $\mathrm{Ba}^{2+}$, $\mathrm{Y}^{3+}$, and $\mathrm{Zr}^{4+}$ and Their Electronic Properties: a Density Functional Theory Study }


